#

Banana Waffles

20 min
$5.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEgg

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastEasySweet

Description

Fluffy and delicious, these banana waffles are a delightful breakfast treat!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • baking powder: 2 tsp
  • salt: 1/4 tsp
  • sugar: 2 tbsp
  • milk: 1 cup
  • ripe bananas: 2, mashed
  • egg: 1
  • vegetable oil: 2 tbsp
  • vanilla extract: 1 tsp
